name: gixig
description: The Hook: Elias is a junior dev for a massive DAO (Decentralized Autonomous Organization). Late one night, while using a dispersal tool to distribute quarterly rewards to 5,000 users, he realizes—one second after clicking "Send"—that he accidentally swapped the "Amount" and "Wallet Address" columns in his spreadsheet.
